1:06:32.040 --> 1:06:33.200
 of things like fibromyalgia

1:06:33.200 --> 1:06:35.000
 and are starting to arrive at treatments.

1:06:35.000 --> 1:06:37.040
 Now, I'm not a physician, I'm a professor,

1:06:37.040 --> 1:06:38.560
