 And in the long term, that's bad.

1:11:21.600 --> 1:11:26.600
 And it can secrete anti-inflammatory cytokines like IL-10.

1:11:27.320 --> 1:11:30.660
 And these matrix metalloproteases, it's kind of a mouthful,

